veronica
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the former generic name, and popular general name, for (members of) the genus Hebe. esp. Hebe salisifolia;=KOROMIKO
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:also koromiko
Pronunciation:
